OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPope and senior protestants
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdenounce anti-gay laws     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pope Francis and the leaders of        
OL,6, protestant churches in England and     
OL,7, Scotland have denounced the            
OL,8, criminalisation of homosexuality.      
OL,10,FSpeaking to reporters after visiting   
OL,11,FSouth Sudan, the Pope said such laws   
OL,12,Fwere a sin and "an injustice".         
OL,14,FHe added people with "homosexual       
OL,15,Ftendencies" are children of God and    
OL,16,Fshould be welcomed by their churches.  
OL,18,FHis comments were backed by the        
OL,19,FArchbishop of Canterbury and the       
OL,20,FModerator of the Church of Scotland.   
